This is a reference implementation, not a distributed SDK. This repository
demonstrates one way to integrate the Platform API in a .NET solution —
architecture patterns, OAuth/PKCE flow, typed clients, Blazor components.
It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially supported by
YouVersion or Life.Church, and is not published as an installable package.
To use the platform, obtain your own App Key and review the platform's
Developer Terms of Use at developers.youversion.com. This code is provided
as-is for educational/reference purposes; clone and adapt it for your own
project rather than treating it as a dependency. The included Blazor reader
components are a minimal integration demo of the Platform API's reading/
highlighting endpoints, not a Bible-reading application in their own right,
and are not intended to replicate or compete with the YouVersion Bible App.

The `BiblePlatform.UsfmReferences` package is an independent, unofficial
C# port of youversion/usfm-references (https://github.com/YouVersion/usfm-references),
an MIT-licensed Python library. It is not affiliated with or endorsed by
YouVersion.
